    Scope and Contents
Schrom, immigrant from Austria, discusses her medical education, internship, and her pediatric residency and training in Austria and in the United States. She also recalls work at St. John's Hospital Perinatal Center in Springfield, outreach programs and regional centers.1 tape, 90 mins., 31 pp.
Interview by Melinda Kwedar, 1976
